Sentencas: The high operating temperature requirement of solid oxide fuel cells demands electrolyte materials stable at temperatures around 800 degrees C.
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of Ca-substituted YAlO3 by pechini route for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The perovskite material YAlO3, with yttrium ion on the A-site and the aluminium ion on the B-site is being investigated as an electrolyte for solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of Ca-substituted YAlO3 by pechini route for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: This work investigates the structure and electrical conductivity of undoped and Ca-doped YAlO3 compositions that has been synthesized by the Pechini route.
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of Ca-substituted YAlO3 by pechini route for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The samples have been investigated by X-ray diffraction studies.
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of Ca-substituted YAlO3 by pechini route for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The electrical conductivity studies have been performed using a.c impedance spectroscopy in the range 200-800 degrees C in air.
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of Ca-substituted YAlO3 by pechini route for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The doped YAlO3 of composition x = 0.1 exhibits a total conductivity of about 2.2 mS/cm at 800 degrees C.
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of Ca-substituted YAlO3 by pechini route for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The microstructural evaluation of the samples has been conducted by scanning electron microscopy coupled with energy dispersive spectrum analysis.
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of Ca-substituted YAlO3 by pechini route for solid oxide fuel cells
